<br /> Chn phn <strong>Role-Based Strategy</strong>. Save li</p><p><strong>Bc 3:</strong> Truy cp: <strong>Manage Jenkins &gt; Manage and Assign Roles</strong><br /> Click vo phn <strong>Manage Roles</strong>. Ta s thy hin ti c mt role admin, role admin ny c cp full tt c mi quyn<br /> C 2 loi Role  y bao gm:<br />  Global roles: Cc role ny c tm nh hng ti ton b h thng, ngha l nu mt User A c gn role X c quyn build job, th User A ny c kh nng build mi job ca mi Project.<br />  Project roles: Cc role ny c tm nh hng  mc thp hn. V d ta c mt role tn l tester_of_staging (c quyn build app), set pattern l <strong>staging</strong>. Th nu user c gn role \"tester_of_staging\" th n c th build cho mi job c cha pattern ny.</p><p>V d ta c th to mt role cho <strong>tester</strong> ch c cc quyn <strong>Build Cancel Read</strong> tt c cc job (nu mun ch hn ch mt vi project no  ta c th s dng <strong>Pattern</strong>)<br /> <strong>Ch : </strong><br />  admin full quyn khng c chnh sa g thm<br /> Gn thm quyn <strong>Overall / Read</strong> cho cc nhm roles khc.</p><h2>Assign role cho User</h2><p> gn quyn hn cho mt i tng user, ta truy cp vo <strong>Manage Jenkins &gt; Manage and Assign Roles &gt; Assign Roles</strong></p><p></p><p>Tham kho:<a href=\"https://viblo.asia/p/continuous-integration-with-jenkins-bai-2-cai-dat-va-cau-hinh-jenkins-L4x5xRwYZBM\">https://viblo.asia/p/continuous-integration-with-jenkins-bai-2-cai-dat-va-cau-hinh-jenkins-L4x5xRwYZBM</a></p><p></p>','RE: Phn quyn user trong Jenkins','','publish','open','closed','','re-phan-quyen-user-trong-jenkins','','','2018-01-19 09:45:32','2018-01-19 09:45:32','',132,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/answer/re-phan-quyen-user-trong-jenkins/',0,'answer','',0),(135,4,'2018-01-19 09:41:39','2018-01-19 09:41:39','You answered on question \"Phn quyn user trong Jenkins\"','post_answer','','publish','open','closed','','post_answer-10','','','2018-01-19 09:41:39','2018-01-19 09:41:39','',134,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/changelog/post_answer-10/