-01-29 10:24:14','2018-01-29 10:24:14','Bi ton: Chng ta to v s dng rt nhiu vm  trn server. Nu mun qun l chng v d bt / tt, ... chng ta phi ssh ln server v g lnh. Vy c tool no c giao din kt ni remote ti server  qun l d dng hn khng?','Lm th no  qun l cm vm (virtualbox) t xa','','inherit','closed','closed','','163-revision-v1','','','2018-01-29 10:24:14','2018-01-29 10:24:14','',163,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/2018/01/29/163-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(228,4,'2018-01-29 10:24:14','2018-01-29 10:24:14','You question on question \"\" was edited','edit_question','','publish','open','closed','','edit_question-18','','','2018-01-29 10:24:14','2018-01-29 10:24:14','',163,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/changelog/edit_question-18/',0,'changelog','',0),(229,4,'2018-01-30 03:16:09','2018-01-30 03:16:09','Ci t kafka trn ubuntu 16.04','Ci t kafka trn ubuntu 16.04','','publish','open','closed','','cai-dat-kafka-tren-ubuntu-16-04','','','2018-01-30 03:16:09','2018-01-30 03:16:09','',0,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/question/cai-dat-kafka-tren-ubuntu-16-04/',0,'question','',0),(230,4,'2018-01-30 03:16:09','2018-01-30 03:16:09','Your posted a question \"\" ','post_question','','publish','open','closed','','post_question-18','','','2018-01-30 03:16:09','2018-01-30 03:16:09','',229,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/changelog/post_question-18/',0,'changelog','',0),(231,4,'2018-01-30 03:16:44','2018-01-30 03:16:44','<h1>Ci t</h1><p></p><h2>Step 1  Install Java</h2><p><code>sudo apt-get update</code></p><p>sudo apt-get install default-jre</p><h2>Step 2  Install ZooKeeper</h2><p><code>sudo apt-get install zookeeperd</code><br /> Check:<br /> <code>netstat -ant | grep :2181</code></p><h2>Step 3  Download and Extract Kafka Binaries</h2><p>Download kafka v my</p><p>Chn server  download : <a href=\"http://www.apache.org/mirrors/\">http://www.apache.org/mirrors/</a><br /> Sau  vo th mc kafka v chn phin bn ph hp v download:<br /> <code>wget http://apache.mirror.amaze.com.au/kafka/0.10.2.1/kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1.tgz</code></p><p>Gii nn vo th mc <code>/opt</code><br /> <code>tar -xvzf kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1.tgz</code></p><h2>Step 4  Configure the Kafka Server</h2><p>Mc nh kafka khng cho delete topic.  s dng n ta sa file <code>config/server.properties</code><br /> <code>delete.topic.enable = true</code></p><h2>Step 5  Start the Kafka Server</h2><p>To th mc  ch logs<br /> <code>mkdir logs</code></p><p>Start server s dng nohup:<br /> <code>nohup bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties &gt; logs/kafka.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</code></p><p>Ta c th kim tra qu trnh start trong file log logs/kafka.log<br /> Sau khi khi ng hon tt kafka s lng nghe  port 9092</p><h2>Step 6  Test the Installation</h2><p>Chng ta s to mt topic TutorialTopic gi v nhn message t n  test kafka</p><p>Publish \"Hello, World\" ti topic TutorialTopic (nu topic cha c kafka s t to topic):<br /> <code>echo \"Hello, World\" | bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic TutorialTopic &gt; /dev/null</code></p><p> nhn message ta to consumer:<br /> <code>bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --topic TutorialTopic --from-beginning</code></p><h2>Step 7  Install KafkaT (Optional)</h2><p><strong>KafkaT</strong> l mt tool t Airbnb cho php ta xem chi tit v kafka cluster ca chng ta v cng c th thc hin mt s lnh qun tr t command line. N s dng ruby nn chng ta cn ci ruby trc:<br /><code>sudo apt-get install ruby ruby-dev build-essential</code></p><p>Ci t KafkaT s dng gem:<br /><code>sudo gem install kafkat --source https://rubygems.org --no-ri --no-rdoc</code></p><p>To file config cho KafkaT<br /> <code>vi ~/.kafkatcfg</code></p><p>{</p><p>\"kafka_path\": \"/opt/kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1\",</p><p>\"log_path\": \"/tmp/kafka-logs\",</p><p>\"zk_path\": \"localhost:2181\"</p><p>}</p><p><br /> By gi ta c th s dng kafkaT:</p><p>View details about all Kafka partitions:<br /> <code>kafkat partitions</code></p><p>Topic Partition Leader Replicas ISRs</p><p>TutorialTopic 0 0 [0] [0]</p><p>Xem chi tit cch s dng: <a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/kafkat\">https://github.com/airbnb/kafkat</a></p><p>Tham kho:<a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-apache-kafka-on-ubuntu-14-04\">https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-apache-kafka-on-ubuntu-14-04</a></p>','RE: Ci t kafka trn ubuntu 16.04','','publish','open','closed','','re-cai-dat-kafka-tren-ubuntu-16-04','','','2018-01-30 03:18:37','2018-01-30 03:18:37','',229,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/answer/re-cai-dat-kafka-tren-ubuntu-16-04/',0,'answer','',0),(232,4,'2018-01-30 03:16:44','2018-01-30 03:16:44','You answered on question \"Ci t kafka trn ubuntu 16.04\"','post_answer','','publish','open','closed','','post_answer-20','','','2018-01-30 03:16:44','2018-01-30 03:16:44','',231,'http://blog.sigma-global.net/changelog/post_answer-20/',0,'changelog','',0),(233,4,'2018-01-30 03:18:05','2018-01-30 03:18:05','<h1>Ci t</h1><p></p><h2>Step 1  Install Java</h2><p><code>sudo apt-get update<br />\nsudo apt-get install default-jre</code></p><h2>Step 2  Install ZooKeeper</h2><p><code>sudo apt-get install zookeeperd</code><br /> Check:<br /> <code>netstat -ant | grep :2181</code></p><h2>Step 3  Download and Extract Kafka Binaries</h2><p>Download kafka v my</p><p>Chn server  download : <a href=\"http://www.apache.org/mirrors/\">http://www.apache.org/mirrors/</a><br /> Sau  vo th mc kafka v chn phin bn ph hp v download:<br /> <code>wget http://apache.mirror.amaze.com.au/kafka/0.10.2.1/kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1.tgz</code></p><p>Gii nn vo th mc <code>/opt</code><br /> <code>tar -xvzf kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1.tgz</code></p><h2>Step 4  Configure the Kafka Server</h2><p>Mc nh kafka khng cho delete topic.  s dng n ta sa file <code>config/server.properties</code><br /> <code>delete.topic.enable = true</code></p><h2>Step 5  Start the Kafka Server</h2><p>To th mc  ch logs<br /> <code>mkdir logs</code></p><p>Start server s dng nohup:<br /> <code>nohup bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/server.properties &gt; logs/kafka.log 2&gt;&amp;1 &amp;</code></p><p>Ta c th kim tra qu trnh start trong file log logs/kafka.log<br /> Sau khi khi ng hon tt kafka s lng nghe  port 9092</p><h2>Step 6  Test the Installation</h2><p>Chng ta s to mt topic TutorialTopic gi v nhn message t n  test kafka</p><p>Publish \"Hello, World\" ti topic TutorialTopic (nu topic cha c kafka s t to topic):<br /> <code>echo \"Hello, World\" | bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --broker-list localhost:9092 --topic TutorialTopic &gt; /dev/null</code></p><p> nhn message ta to consumer:<br /> <code>bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --zookeeper localhost:2181 --topic TutorialTopic --from-beginning</code></p><h2>Step 7  Install KafkaT (Optional)</h2><p><strong>KafkaT</strong> l mt tool t Airbnb cho php ta xem chi tit v kafka cluster ca chng ta v cng c th thc hin mt s lnh qun tr t command line. N s dng ruby nn chng ta cn ci ruby trc:<br /><code>sudo apt-get install ruby ruby-dev build-essential</code></p><p>Ci t KafkaT s dng gem:<br /> s<code>udo gem install kafkat --source https://rubygems.org --no-ri --no-rdoc</code></p><p>To file config cho KafkaT<br /> <code>vi ~/.kafkatcfg<br />\n{<br />\n\"kafka_path\": \"/opt/kafka_2.10-0.10.2.1\",<br />\n\"log_path\": \"/tmp/kafka-logs\",<br />\n\"zk_path\": \"localhost:2181\"<br />\n}<br />\n</code><br /> By gi ta c th s dng kafkaT:</p><p>View details about all Kafka partitions:<br /> <code>kafkat partitions<br />\nTopic           Partition   Leader      Replicas        ISRs<br />\nTutorialTopic   0             0           [0]           [0]</code></p><p>Xem chi tit cch s dng: <a href=\"https://github.com/airbnb/kafkat\">https://github.com/airbnb/kafkat</a></p><p>Tham kho:<a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-apache-kafka-on-ubuntu-14-04\">https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-apache-kafka-on-ubuntu-14-04</a></p>','RE: Ci t kafka trn ubuntu 16.04','','inherit','closed','closed','','231-revision-v1',